text: Aart van Wilgenburg (16 September 1902 - 22 December 1955) was a Dutch swimmer. He competed in the men's 100 metre backstroke event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1955 deaths Category:Dutch male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of the Netherlands Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Amsterdam Category:Male backstroke swimmers
